OL,7, If you go away on holiday and take your
OL,8, pet with you - watch out forCquarantine
OL,9,CkennelsGon your return...              
OL,11, According to anti-quarantine group,    
OL,12,CPassport for Pets,Ganimals are left in 
OL,13, "dirty, windowless cells, denied basic 
OL,14, welfare needs and treated abhorrently  
OL,15, for their six months behind bars".     
OL,17, Go Green examines the allegations and  
OL,18, questions whetherCalternative measures 
OL,19, would make adequate rabies deterrents. 
