OL,7, Passport for Pets alleges many kennels 
OL,8, and catteries are failing to provide   
OL,9, adequate veterinary care, leaving pets 
OL,10,Cdeprived of exerciseGand human contact.
OL,12, The group claims owners are being      
OL,13,Ccharged for non-existent facilities    
OL,14, such as heating in the winter.         
OL,16, At presentCRSPCA inspectorsGhave no    
OL,17, right of access to the 80 privately    
OL,18, operated quarantine kennels in the UK. 
