OL,5,C"CRUELLA KENNELS"             Q"S|~ 
OL,6,G                                       
OL,7,GTheCstandard of accommodationGin       
OL,8,Gquarantine kennels is a major concern  
OL,9,Gto pet owners, says Tracy Mathews from 
OL,10,GPassport for Pets:                     
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,G"Many cats and dogs sufferCinjuries to 
OL,13,Cpaws and tailsGagainst the concrete    
OL,14,Gwalls and floors of their small        
OL,15,Genclosures.                            
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,G"Enclosures are often cold, damp and   
OL,18,Gfilthy with excrement causing great    
OL,19,Cdistress to the animals."Gshe explains.
