OL,7,CLynne Cohen,GfromCBurnley,Gwas appalled
OL,8,Gat the lack of attention and care her  
OL,9,Gcats received whilst in quarantine.    
OL,10,G                                       
OL,11,GShe says: "My four cats wereCravenously
OL,12,ChungryGwhenever I visited them. My     
OL,13,Ginstructions about their diet and      
OL,14,Gkeeping the cats together were         
OL,15,Gcompletely ignored.                    
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,G"Eventually we wereCforced to move our 
OL,18,Ccats to another catteryGat great       
OL,19,Gexpense, where the care was better."   
