OL,7,CDiane Williamson,GfromCDevon,Gwhose    
OL,8, 14-month-old golden retriever died in  
OL,9, quarantine, believes if "Jess" had been
OL,10, treated sooner, she would have had a   
OL,11, better chance of survival.             
OL,13, She says: "Instead, the proprietor and 
OL,14, vet wereCoff-hand and uncommunicative."
OL,16,CEileen Thompson,GofCBucks,Gwho also    
OL,17, lost a dog in quarantine, adds: "It    
OL,18, appears kennels can allow dogs to die  
OL,19, without any sort of explanation."      
