OL,7,CLouise Redmond,GfromCHounslow,Gsays    
OL,8,Gquarantine kennels are "perfectly good 
OL,9,Gplaces to send your pets".             
OL,10,G                                       
OL,11,GShe adds: "My labrador was placed in   
OL,12,Gone after came back from aG            
OL,13,Gworking-holiday in India. She wasCso   
OL,14,Cwell cared forGthat she didn't want to 
OL,15,Gcome home with me when her stay was up.
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,G"Though I disliked the idea of her in  
OL,18,Gone, I preferred that thanCthe prospect
OL,19,Cof her spreading rabies."              
