OL,6,G                                       
OL,7,GPassport for Pets believes there are   
OL,8,Gmodern, humane methods of preventing   
OL,9,CrabiesGfrom entering the UK.           
OL,10,G                                       
OL,11,GSpokeswoman Tracy Mathews says:        
OL,12,G"There'sCimmunisation,Gwhich is close  
OL,13,Gto 100% effective.                     
OL,14,G                                       
OL,15,G"In addition, animals that come from   
OL,16,Grabies-free countries pose no threat,  
OL,17,Gand should be admitted without         
OL,18,Gquarantine  - so long as they are      
OL,19,GproperlyCidentified,"Gshe adds.        
