OL,7, A Ministry of Agriculture spokesman    
OL,8, saidCquarantine regulationsGwere       
OL,9, under review.                          
OL,11, "Ministers are considering a microchip 
OL,12, vaccination passport instead of        
OL,13, quarantine.                            
OL,15, "At present, there isCno law governing 
OL,16,Cthe welfare of animals in quarantine   
OL,17,Ckennels.GHowever the Government        
OL,18, intends to change this."               
